br />\n節錄自黃子華, 拾下拾下, 而家我成日都會同身邊人分享<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=anvg_iEgK6U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Danvg_iEgK6U&d=xhUaz24d73f8t0McE10xip4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=98d73c23\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=anvg_iEgK6U</a><br />\n<br />\n人o既慾望係無限, 你唔調節自己o既心理, 一世都唔會開心同覺得足夠<br />\n有時間就要諗下自己所有o既, 唔好諗自己未有o既<br />\n<br />\n不過我都唔成功,<br />\n我未出黎做野果時, 覺得自己搵1皮都會好心滿意足<br />\n但出左黎做野, 就被個社會建設左我<br />\n到有咁上下收入, 又會諗買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcabae673dc92f57ab364d4211b4aac3f25ffecd","tid":817683,"uid":42314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T01:58:07.000Z","msg":"80-100k monthly"},{"pid":"d1aa7881f9a0c1d82ce0fb668db144bc27388276","tid":817683,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T02:00:22.000Z","msg":"去教會教會答到你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搵多多都唔夠你奉獻啊 on9 ! <br />\n返教會嘅話你點都唔夠錢洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> /member]"},{"pid":"51dad2feb3ebefb3324e8225a08b493e70da0da0","tid":817683,"uid":90946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T02:06:09.000Z","msg":"錢無人嫌多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但現實係夠供到層樓養到架車仔，搞掂埋四大長老同仔女<br />\n年年都去到旅行，個個月有錢食一兩餐好野咪ok囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣無十萬八萬都唔掂"},{"pid":"0f032b3172b6aeabc5a25aa81ce92d9b096465c5","tid":817683,"uid":173814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T02:06:42.000Z","msg":"有研究指出過，大約係月入6萬至8萬之後既收入，對你既happiness影響就開始有diminishing returns"},{"pid":"b7c97b51eb037b9706470be11c1b5b9fcaa10583","tid":817683,"uid":65424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T02:08:10.000Z","msg":